   *
   * @see {@link https://hono.dev/docs/api/hono#not-found}
   *
   * @param {NotFoundHandler} handler - request handler for not-found
   * @returns {Hono} changed Hono instance
   *
   * @example
   * ```ts
   * app.notFound((c) => {
   *   return c.text('Custom 404 Message', 404)
   * })
   * ```
   */
